abstract: >
  A curated, scored, and weekly-updated list of AI agent harnesses, orchestration
  frameworks, coding-agent products, meta-prompting/skill stacks, evaluation
  harnesses, and SDKs. Projects are classified across nine categories and ranked
  by relevance to harness concerns (environment, orchestration, lifecycle,
  guardrails) alongside GitHub activity signals.
